{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775860927796,"sessionID":"ses_286712c12ffeTK8U7ji6J8muJA","part":{"id":"prt_d798f4d32001REMDTmvyccSCne","messageID":"msg_d798f3d2700109mRCBPIu3Yvcg","sessionID":"ses_286712c12ffeTK8U7ji6J8muJA","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860993879,"sessionID":"ses_286712c12ffeTK8U7ji6J8muJA","part":{"id":"prt_d79904ef5001sxBLTMlIEXRKTc","messageID":"msg_d798f3d2700109mRCBPIu3Yvcg","sessionID":"ses_286712c12ffeTK8U7ji6J8muJA","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-05f12f09c34343eb81e92f06dcb448b7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/picod`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify AuthManager struct matches design specification\n- [ ] Verify AuthManager has publicKey *rsa.PublicKey field\n- [ ] Verify AuthManager has mutex sync.RWMutex field\n- [ ] Verify NewAuthManager() function exists with correct signature\n- [ ] Verify ValidateToken() method exists with correct signature\n- [ ] Verify no additional unintended fields or methods are present\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/auth.go structure against design.md line 181-192\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: Verify AuthClaims struct matches design specification\n- [ ] Verify AuthClaims embeds jwt.RegisteredClaims\n- [ ] Verify no additional custom claims are present\n- [ ] Verify struct is exported (capital A)\n- [ ] Verify struct is in pkg/picod/auth.go\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/auth.go line 16-18\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Verify NewAuthManager implementation\n- [ ] Verify function reads PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY environment variable\n- [ ] Verify missing public key returns ErrInvalidPublicKey with correct message\n- [ ] Verify PEM decoding uses pem.Decode() correctly\n- [ ] Verify invalid PEM format returns appropriate error\n- [ ] Verify public key parsing uses x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey()\n- [ ] Verify RSA type validation with type assertion\n- [ ] Verify non-RSA key returns appropriate error\n- [ ] Verify klog.Info() logs \"Auth manager initialized successfully\"\n- [ ] Verify AuthManager is returned with publicKey set\n- [ ] Verify mutex is initialized but not used in NewAuthManager\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/auth.go NewAuthManager() implementation line 25-51\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Verify ValidateToken implementation\n- [ ] Verify method acquires read lock with mutex.RLock()\n- [ ] Verify read lock is deferred with mutex.RUnlock()\n- [ ] Verify jwt.ParseWithClaims is called with AuthClaims\n- [ ] Verify signing method checks for *jwt.SigningMethodRSA\n- [ ] Verify non-RSA method returns error\n- [ ] Verify publicKey is returned from verification callback\n- [ ] Verify jwt.WithLeeway(1*time.Minute) is applied\n- [ ] Verify token validation errors are wrapped with ErrInvalidToken\n- [ ] Verify valid token returns *AuthClaims\n- [ ] Verify invalid claims return ErrInvalidToken\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/auth.go ValidateToken() implementation line 53-73\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Verify AuthMiddleware function signature and structure\n- [ ] Verify function accepts *AuthManager parameter\n- [ ] Verify function returns gin.HandlerFunc\n- [ ] Verify middleware closure captures authManager\n- [ ] Verify middleware function accepts *gin.Context\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/middleware.go AuthMiddleware() function\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: Verify Authorization header extraction logic\n- [ ] Verify HeaderAuthorization constant is used to get header\n- [ ] Verify missing header check returns ErrMissingAuthHeader\n- [ ] Verify HandleError() is called with correct error\n- [ ] Verify c.Abort() is called after error\n- [ ] Verify early return after abort\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/middleware.go line 13-18\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Verify Bearer token format validation\n- [ ] Verify strings.HasPrefix checks for \"Bearer \" prefix\n- [ ] Verify invalid format returns ErrInvalidAuthFormat\n- [ ] Verify HandleError() is called with correct error\n- [ ] Verify c.Abort() is called after error\n- [ ] Verify early return after abort\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/middleware.go line 20-24\n\n---\n\n### Task 8: Verify token extraction and validation\n- [ ] Verify token string extraction with TrimPrefix\n- [ ] Verify authManager.ValidateToken() is called\n- [ ] Verify validation errors are logged with klog.Warningf\n- [ ] Verify HandleError() is called on validation failure\n- [ ] Verify c.Abort() is called on validation failure\n- [ ] Verify early return after abort\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/middleware.go line 26-33\n\n---\n\n### Task 9: Verify successful authentication handling\n- [ ] Verify claims are stored in Gin context with c.Set(\"claims\", claims)\n- [ ] Verify http.MaxBytesReader is applied to request body\n- [ ] Verify MaxBodySize constant is used (32MB)\n- [ ] Verify c.Next() is called to continue request chain\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/middleware.go line 35-38\n\n---\n\n### Task 10: Verify authentication error constants are defined\n- [ ] Verify ErrMissingAuthHeader constant exists with correct value\n- [ ] Verify ErrInvalidAuthFormat constant exists with correct value\n- [ ] Verify ErrInvalidToken constant exists with correct value\n- [ ] Verify ErrInvalidSignature constant exists (if used)\n- [ ] Verify ErrTokenExpired constant exists (if used)\n- [ ] Verify ErrInvalidPublicKey constant exists\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/errors.go for authentication error constants\n\n---\n\n### Task 11: Verify error message constants are defined\n- [ ] Verify ErrMsgMissingAuthHeader constant exists\n- [ ] Verify ErrMsgInvalidAuthFormat constant exists\n- [ ] Verify ErrMsgInvalidToken constant exists\n- [ ] Verify messages match design specification\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/constants.go for error message constants\n\n---\n\n### Task 12: Verify environment variable constant is defined\n- [ ] Verify PublicKeyEnvVar constant exists with value \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"\n- [ ] Verify HeaderAuthorization constant exists with value \"Authorization\"\n- [ ] Verify MaxBodySize constant exists with value 32 << 20 (32MB)\n\n**Verification**: R