decoding uses pem.Decode() correctly\n35: - [ ] Verify invalid PEM format returns appropriate error\n36: - [ ] Verify public key parsing uses x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey()\n37: - [ ] Verify RSA type validation with type assertion\n38: - [ ] Verify non-RSA key returns appropriate error\n39: - [ ] Verify klog.Info() logs \"Auth manager initialized successfully\"\n40: - [ ] Verify AuthManager is returned with publicKey set\n41: - [ ] Verify mutex is initialized but not used in NewAuthManager\n42: \n43: **Verification**: Review pkg/picod/auth.go NewAuthManager() implementation line 25-51\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ### Task 4: Verify ValidateToken implementation\n48: - [ ] Verify method acquires read lock with mutex.RLock()\n49: - [ ] Verify read lock is deferred with mutex.RUnlock()\n50: - [ ] Verify jwt.ParseWithClaims is called with AuthClaims\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 502. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/picod`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify AuthManager struct matches design specification\n- [ ] Verify AuthManager has publicKey *rsa.PublicKey field\n- [ ] Verify AuthManager has mutex sync.RWMutex field\n- [ ] Verify NewAuthManager() function exists with correct signature\n- [ ] Verify ValidateToken() method exists with correct signature\n- [ ] Verify no additional unintended fields or methods are present\n\n**Verification**: Review pkg/picod/auth.go structure against design.md line 181-192\n\n---\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775860997251,"end":1775860997268}}}}
